text.tspan: Two Delay lines, which can be Skewed independently to create a Stereo Delay.
Reverb effect can be enriched with a Chorus-like effect.
Pitch secondary function: set the maximum Chorus effect.
Size secondary function: set the amount of Delay signal into Reverb.
Overlap secondary function: set the amount of Dry signal into Reverb.
Blend secondary function: set the Left signal level.
Window secondary function: set the Right signal level.
For QuBit Nebulae v.2 - By Ian Hoogeboom
